Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:02.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:33.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:40.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers who keep\Na close eye on the countless souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,good and evil, that fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:46.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen, who has brought chaos\Nupon the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:48.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to set his plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancars, created by Aizen\Nusing the Hogyoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a material that removes the boundaries\Nbetween Soul Reapers and Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,appear in Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:07.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I deny you...\Nso now you'll get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:17.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ulquiorra and Yammy defeat Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:21.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Urahara and Yoruichi manage\Nto drive them back in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo falls into a depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:29.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but before him appears\NCaptain Hitsugaya's advance guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who have been sent from Soul Society\Nto confront the Arrancars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:38.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those guys who beat you up\Nthe other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:45.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,More precisely,\Nthere are three classes within the Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is the "Gillian."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The second is "Adjuchas."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the third is "Vasto Lordes."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the top class within\Nthe Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are equal to humans in size.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:05.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are said to be only a few of them\Nwithin Hueco Mundo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:13.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These Vasto Lordes are stronger\Nthan our Soul Reaper captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:18.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Aizen now has more than\Nten of these Vasto Lorde
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under his control...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the end of Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have returned...Lord Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Ulquiorra...\NYammy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:44.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me of your achievements...\Nin front of your 20 brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me, Ulquiorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:58.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...what you saw and felt in\Nthe World of the Living, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:39.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why you decided\Nhe was not worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:46.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Your orders were to "kill him\Nif he proved to be a hindrance to us."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How soft of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:54.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've squashed those bastards\Nwith my first blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if "kill him" was a part\Nof the order,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:05.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been best to kill him,\Nof course! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree...\Nwhatever the case, he's the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There may have been\Nno reason to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was even less reason\Nto let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, Yammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were beaten up pretty bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You may say\Nhe wasn't worth killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but it just sounds like\Nyou couldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who beat me up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,were the guy wearing clogs\Nand the dark-skinned girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I would have killed\Nthose two with one blow as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:37.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:45.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that our problem\Nisn't this guy as he is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:51.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What Lord Aizen is worried about\Nis not this guy as he is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but this guy's rate of growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,True, his potential powers\Nwere amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:01.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were as unstable\Nas they were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave things as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's a chance of him\Neither destroying himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or that we could bring him\Nunder our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came back\Nwithout killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm saying you're soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:17.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets bigger than you predict\Nand turns against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you plan to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens,\NI'll get rid of him. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't complain about that,\Ncan you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:31.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well... That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want...Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:58.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is that really going to get it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... It's out! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... It just seems so yucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Candy came out\Nso easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is made simply,\Nor should I say poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's the Department of Research...\N- Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- and Development for you, very unique.\N- Hey, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you guys\Ngoing back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\Nwe're not going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:27.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stay until our fight\Nwith the Arrancars is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! You're staying?\NBut where are you going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make this clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:35.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough space\Nto keep all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Not even me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yikes! If you think about it,\Nyou're the last person I'd allow to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For that matter,\NI have no idea why you would think
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd let you stay in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You may undo a button,\Nbut what's impossible is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even if you lift your skirt a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I will not give in\Nto temptation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man who never gives in\Nto temptation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nwhy don't you close your fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:12.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now...\NI'll have Orihime put me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:17.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NDid you already get her permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:21.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, but she's the type\Nthat just can't say "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:26.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--? Inoue and Rangiku will be\Nsleeping in the same room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful\Nforbidden flower garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a little mascot\Nfor your flower gard-!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come too, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd go, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come! It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have somewhere to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And most of all,\NI won't depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a place to stay on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:01.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better...\Nkeep that wooden sword hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:05.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be going to\NMr. Urahara's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to live off\Nof him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to\Nask him about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Where do you plan to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Rukia!\N- Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only place for me, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?!\NMy family has seen you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What excuse are you planning\Nto give them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a Hollow...\NShall we take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it. Too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that Soul Reaper Kurumadani\Nor whatever in charge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But for a Hollow,\Nit smells a little funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:23.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I keep worrying over it?\NI feel stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know, Kurosaki\Nhas recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:40.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...\NKuchiki is really something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm...a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,KUROSAKI CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you see.\NI've lost everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my place to stay and\Nmy money for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let her stay here, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:12.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it, Yuzu!\NThat's exactly what I was thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:15.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as long as you like, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...\NKeep that thumb hidden, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll catch on to your act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Listen to me, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:29.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I now have a third daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, judging from\Nthe way he's acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no sign\Nhe has any doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:41.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It hit me in that instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A uniform, depending on\Nwho's wearing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,can become a lethal blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like an invincible blade
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:50.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that can shred our steel armor\Nof logic into nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you pipe down?\NI'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- You have no reaction at all?\N- Ah, no... I don't mean you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really going to leave\Nyou behind, Mr. Asano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being so formal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...! I saw this really\Nrealistic monster up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop that, Mr. Asano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:39.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to stay over? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, but... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Great answer!\N- O-Ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I love\Nabout you, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, can I take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All the excitement today\Ngot me all sweaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in my cleavage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... The bathroom's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join me, Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already had my-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch! That hurts Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have nowhere else to go,\Nyou can come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:15.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Noisy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, but a little small...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.\NI don't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:44.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... Why are you so down today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:50.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-I'm not down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk to me about it.\NI'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:58.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...but...I'm not down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't talk to me,\NI'll do something painful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I was so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And next time, I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki is...really something,\Nisn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:29.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki was so depressed for\Nso long but she cheered him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:35.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave him a swift boot...\Nand made him perk up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:45.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:52.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Kurosaki to cheer up.\NThat's all I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:03.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When Kuchiki came back\Nand cheered up Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been really happy,\Nand yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:11.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:20.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...I-I'm jealous...\Nof Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:26.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki is kind and gentle...\Nstrong and pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and she cheered up Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:34.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like her...but why am I so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like this in school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I return home\Nand I'm alone, I'm a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:48.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... This is so embarrassing!\NI'm terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:58.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...giku...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow-ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:12.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle-tickle-tickle-\Ntickle-tickle-tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! Rangiku-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Oh, I hit my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:28.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girl...\NYou should just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Kuchiki both...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is still a kid\Nwho can't stand up by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:39.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he needs both\Nyou and Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you're trying your best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to come to terms with\Nyour serious emotions, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so much easier to run away\Nfrom those emotions;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,tossing them at the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing firm,\Ntrying to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really cool,\Nyou know...Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...\NLet it all out, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry on my chest, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't let anyone see you,\NI hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:39.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt strong Spiritual Pressure\Nfrom several sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't match Ulquiorra's report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the Pesquisa\Nall the way up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...\NThere are a lot more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they've called for\Nreinforcements from Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they'd nipped it in the bud,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,things wouldn't have gotten\Nso complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:28.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I say you're soft...\NUlquiorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,D Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shawlong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Edrad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:34.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illfort...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakeem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they show even a hint\Nof Spiritual Pressure, capture them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,FOR RUKIA♥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They just gave me\Nyour sister’s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that’s to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to stay in\Nyour closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:05.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me.\NTalk to my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:09.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s why I brought some things\Nto fix up that dingy closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:13.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Bell! Massager!\NA little window!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Worse and worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And didn’t you just slip in\Nthe word “dingy”?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange face…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:48.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you think it’s strange,\NYumichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This…This handmade riceball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re handmade,\Nbut so neat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and packed in\Nthis complicated wrapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re lined up in all the stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:08.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And according to the salesgirl,\Nthey’re replaced several times a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, it’s insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe that salesgirl\Nhas that sort of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:18.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I say there’s somebody\Npulling strings in the background!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to\Nthe same conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:33.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate so much! I’ve had my fill!\NIt was delicious, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn’t look all that great,\Nbut it tasted great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I’m so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I cook,\Nthere’s no one to eat the food
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought maybe there was\Nsomething wrong with my taste buds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! Would you like\Nsome ice cream, Rangiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:58.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put all kinds of toppings on it,\Nit’s even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Delicious!\N– Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have in yours, Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird color!\NBut it might be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yum!\N– Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:34.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you captured them all?\NYou will show them no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:39.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they show even a glimmer\Nof Spiritual Pressure, kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let a single one escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:13.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:18.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,…And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:24.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The blade of your Tensa Zangetsu\Nis as black as your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:27.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Why, your heart is\Nnormally much blacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:28.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:31.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is as pure and white\Nas this zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with that zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The mail is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:40.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:43.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh Seat Yamada,\Nwhat about the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:46.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, they’re addressed\Nto Eighth Seat Ogido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:48.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re mostly from women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:51.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighth Seat Ogido is popular\Nwith women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:54.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! I just can’t understand\Nwhy that guy is so popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:56.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:59.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have many finer points,\NThird Seat Iemura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:01.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For example…?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:02.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Er, uh…\N– Er, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s none…?!